Sardines are a type of fish that can be obtained by cooking a raw sardine on a fire or cooking range, requiring level 1 Cooking and granting 40 experience when successful. Players may burn a sardine while cooking one, resulting in a burnt sardine; the burn rate while cooking these will decrease as players reach higher Cooking levels. It will stop burning entirely at Cooking level 38 on both ranges and fires.

Sardines can be eaten to heal 4 hitpoints.

'''Sardines''' are a type of [[fish]] that can be obtained by cooking a [[raw sardine]] on a [[fire]] or [[cooking range]], requiring level 1 [[Cooking]] and granting 40 experience when successful. Players may burn a sardine while cooking one, resulting in a [[Burnt fish (sardine)|burnt sardine]]; the [[burn rate]] while cooking these will decrease as players reach higher Cooking levels. It will stop burning entirely at [[Cooking]] level 38 on both ranges and fires.

Sardines can be eaten to heal 4 hitpoints.
